  m_text: "Jacob DeWese:\r\nProgramming\r\nBuild Master\r\nLighting & Rendering\r\nLevel
    Design\n\r\nBrielle Jean Baptiste:\r\n3D Environment\r\nLevel Design\r\nStory
    Concept\nUI Layout\nUI Art\n\r\nElizabeth Lourcey:\r\nProgramming\r\nGame Logo\r\nUI
    Art\n\r\nGabriel Maldonado-Martin:\r\n2D Art\r\nPoster\r\nUI Art\r\nStudio Logo\n\r\nMolly
    Seawell:\r\nNarrative Design\r\nUI Layout\r\nUI Art\r\nMusic\r\nSound Design\r\nGame
    Trailer\n\r\nAdditional External Sources Used:\r\nLumenfago - Sketchfab \r\nolhahunchag
    - Sketchfab \r\nHabitaci\xF3n - Sketchfab \r\nVictoria V. - Sketchfab \r\nGracebailey
    - Sketchfab \r\nArtchanny - Gumroad \r\nPhildjii - Itch.io \r\nSorceressGameLab
    - Itch.io"
